original_query: SELECT MIN(n.name) AS member_in_charnamed_movie FROM cast_info AS ci, company_name AS cn, keyword AS k, movie_companies AS mc, movie_keyword AS mk, name AS n, title AS t WHERE cn.country_code ='[us]' AND k.keyword ='character-name-in-title' AND n.id = ci.person_id AND ci.movie_id = t.id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND mk.keyword_id = k.id AND t.id = mc.movie_id AND mc.company_id = cn.id AND ci.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
rewritten_query: CREATE VIEW E6 AS SELECT * FROM name AS name
CREATE VIEW E1 AS SELECT * FROM cast_info AS cast_info
CREATE VIEW E5 AS SELECT * FROM movie_keyword AS movie_keyword
CREATE VIEW E3 AS SELECT * FROM keyword AS keyword WHERE keyword.keyword = 'character-name-in-title'
CREATE UNLOGGED TABLE E5E3 AS SELECT * FROM E5 WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM E3 WHERE E5.keyword_id=E3.id)
CREATE VIEW E4 AS SELECT * FROM movie_companies AS movie_companies
CREATE VIEW E2 AS SELECT * FROM company_name AS company_name WHERE company_name.country_code = '[us]'
CREATE UNLOGGED TABLE E4E2 AS SELECT * FROM E4 WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM E2 WHERE E4.company_id=E2.id)

CREATE UNLOGGED TABLE E5E3E4E2E7 AS SELECT * FROM E5E3 WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM E4E2E7 WHERE E5E3.movie_id=E4E2E7.movie_id)

CREATE UNLOGGED TABLE E6E1E5E3E4E2E7 AS SELECT MIN(name) AS MEMBER_IN_CHARNAMED_MOVIE FROM E6 WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM E1E5E3E4E2E7 WHERE E6.id=E1E5E3E4E2E7.person_id)
